There is a mod installed, called Feed The Beast Utilities, it allows you to chunkload your base, Always do that, especially when playing on a server. Chunkloading your base prevents being robbed or losing stuff. Another great thing about them it that exploding creepers dont destroy blocks anymore. Upon Reaching MV you will get access to AE2, everywhere where you connect your Applied Energisitcs 2 Devices needs to be chunkloaded in order to prevent TPS/FPS Issues and even crashes. Last but not least, remember to never build you multiblocks on chunk boarders, The Issue with them corrupted is easily preventable using chunkloading.
